name: DontLeak
description: Hides DMs whilst screensharing to prevent leaking

name: Narrator Custom
description: Custom narrator options for Vencord using TikTok TTS voices

name: Message Logger Enhanced
description: Message logger that stores messages in persistant storage

name: Better Activities
description: Shows activity icons in the member list and allows showing all activities

name: Follow User
description: Adds a follow option in the user context menu to always be in the same VC as them

name: Ignore Terms
description: Ignore Discord's new terms of service

name: Media Playback Speed
description: Allows changing the (default) playback speed of media embeds

name: Notify User Changes
description: Adds a notify option in the user context menu to get notified when a user changes voice channels or online status

name: Silent Typing Enhanced
description: Hide typing indicator for yourself with support for enable per guild/user

name: Voice Chat Utilities
description: Allows you to perform multiple actions on an entire channel (move, mute, disconnect, etc.)

name: Keyboard Sounds
description: Add keyboard typing sounds, uses sounds packs from Opera GX

name: Who's Watching
description: See who is watching your screenshare
